Ne postoji pravi
razlog što mi nisi pisao, zar ne?

01:14:16.502 --> 01:14:17.419
<i>Za tebe sam uvijek bio
Chesterov mali brat.</i>

01:14:22.507 --> 01:14:23.675
<i>Iskoristila si me,</i>

01:14:27.428 --> 01:14:28.638
<i>da mu se približiš,</i>

01:14:30.515 --> 01:14:31.682
<i>u životu i smrti.</i>

01:15:06.339 --> 01:15:09.592
